claim.claim-text:
1. A compact neutron generator, comprising:
an electron beam source;
a power rod at which an electron beam from said electron beam source is directed, said power rod including at least one neutron multiplying material;
a target isotope;
at least one neutron spectrum shaper disposed between said neutron multiplying material and said target isotope; and
at least one cooling channel disposed around said at least one spectrum shaper and through which a coolant is pumped.
